Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:22.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinose Yayoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Third Chief Clerk of the Ministry of Internal Affairs and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Communications Statistics Office, Second Investigation Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, you can say it without stumbling or mispronouncing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of an elite officer from public safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Sawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shizume.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:49.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, names are just aliases in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:53.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be working with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:55.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You seem displeased.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I do or not doesn't matter. It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this poster will catch your interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:10.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man whom we assume is BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lee Shenshun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:20.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The self-proclaimed Chinese exchange student who was hiding in Shinjuku Okubo two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:25.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:29.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He has been working for the CIA the last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He left the syndicate and is working for the CIA now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:35.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like that's all in the past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:40.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The CIA is also frantically searching for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But his star disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:51.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Unless it's his ghost we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:54.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The details are still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:59.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We are continuing our investigation in order to find out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:03.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:10.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your priority is the capture of BK201, and Shion, Professor Mikhail Pavlichenko's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:16.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The cutie that BK201 is dragging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:32.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How can you resign without telling me...I mean, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you could say I needed a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer have a place with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You called the other day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't get yourself into anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:51.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Kirihara! What-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.43,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,You got her name wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Yayoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Getting information from your friends in public safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:13.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All information from the police, public safety, and the military should all be accessible here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're being frigid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel through your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:28.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your lover won't notice you if you only rely on your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're remaining chaste for BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:35.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Cut this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:44.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, I just got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:54.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To think we are able to see cranes at the ruins of the Heaven's War...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Close the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in the city soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're pooping there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your sphincter a bit too loose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stitch it together already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Something smells...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:40.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be good friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We just recently moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lee Honshik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,These are my siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:01.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They certainly are multicultural...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Smile dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling isn't in my programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To comply with our client's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will train you to be an agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever talk back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:23.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if you want to survive as a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're off by 18cm to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wind velocity: 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 1200.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,2mm to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They'll notice you if you shoot when there is no noise coming from the construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Use your brain a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Change your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look through your scope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,On the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Further down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mobile target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile target...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't shoot that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wind blowing from southeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wind velocity: 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,2mm to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My aim was misaligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a contractor, come up with a better lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't miss this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What a brave girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can she kill someone who's just annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't become someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But let me make this clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the only reason I'm following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:16.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you do any—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to obey my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being a contractor, she's still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hold back, she'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eat whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:48.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He used to eat so much, but now he only drinks alcohol, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Nori-chan, let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we're dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:10.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not dancing because you want to! You're being made to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will happen if we just fool around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We should go and find something bright and shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:19.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Something that will make us feel alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:24.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go with Prof. Norio's sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's all cool, Norio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Will you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:37.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:44.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'd fuck anything that has a hole, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:48.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! Pedophile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Something that makes me feel alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there is no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm staying at a love hotel with a kid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a bad place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the client?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the training about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's a contractor, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you a question then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:43.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been asked to keep track of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:55.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not eating to save money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tear-jerker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This hotel went bankrupt ages ago, so everything is up for grabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it's nutritious, but it'll make you full.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.94,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode 4    The Wavering Ark on the Lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1130,690)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The terrorist attack at Vladivostok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it looked like a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:32.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There was a big mess with lots of casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:35.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that several contractors were involved as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but it's already been covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:44.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the Japanese organization, CIA, and MI6 were all outsmarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are the ones responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This intel isn't worth the price I paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:58.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you want more information, you'd better ask Madame Oreille.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Oreille?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's a legendary informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:07.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she has more ears than the normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I joined Section 3 to learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:26.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I haven't learned a thing about the mystery surrounding BK201,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,nor can I find out anything about the organization I'm working for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:36.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did BK201's star disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make any unnecessary moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the vital points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drop your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Understand your surrounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anything can be used as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Evade the attacks with your upper body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about any other movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,be prepared for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Undulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Draw your stomach in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on your abdominal muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the ocean waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your core muscles are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So is the balance between the abdominal and back muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:44.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Dancing is the best way to train them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:49.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because of the instant ramen I ate yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Time to put your training to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Try escaping without using your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut your trap and do as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, go on, Norio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play doctor with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty cute up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be rude to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be too creeped out by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He has a crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:39.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are we playing tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She had to go and do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving in a way that it couldn't before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:56.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:02.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! She's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:13.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Violence doesn't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the cops are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting crowded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.92,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:42.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July, help Suou escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go and buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Nori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:37.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Uh... Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,just wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want there to be any fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:50.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I should tell you my name first before asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Norio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.16,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,I feel weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Norio. It's written with the "virtue" character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.04,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This sparkling—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you eat something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That face isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:04.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that Noah's Ark is unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:09.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,For all of the animals, only one male and female pair of each species was allowed on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Such arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:15.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So what about the ones who're neither a man nor a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:23.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've just earned the privilege to board the Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tampon with wings prevents leakage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fly without wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Puberty again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's like Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nika?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:58.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! What is it now? Mating season?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Being chased by a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Karma is a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:06.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:14.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he didn't look like him or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:26.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But his aura and expressions were like Nika when he confessed to Tanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's the expression when you're in love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:37.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When Nika confessed, I felt my heart pound with excitement, even though it wasn't to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:41.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But now I don't feel anything even though his feelings were for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:46.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a contractor. Or better yet, you'll understand it when you become a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:49.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a woman already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:56.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You used your ability, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell; even if you hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's pointless to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasant night, isn't it, Ichinose Yayoi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:44.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:50.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you prefer I call you Kirihara Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:11.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:11.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:22.21,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:22.21,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:31.77,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:31.77,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:37.95,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:37.95,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.70,0:22:43.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.70,0:22:43.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.68,0:22:47.81,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.68,0:22:47.81,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.58,0:22:56.46,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.58,0:22:56.46,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:56.28,0:23:01.55,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:22:56.28,0:23:01.55,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.29,0:23:08.50,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.29,0:23:08.50,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:23:08.13,0:23:16.09,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:08.13,0:23:16.09,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:16.01,0:23:26.38,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:16.01,0:23:26.38,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:36.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You lose your emotions when you become a contractor, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:41.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:50.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means being with someone I hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:56.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what it takes to meet Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:02.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The overcast sky is bleak and grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:06.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The time flows too slowly for a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:11.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The unripe fruit remains bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:16.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After you've lost everything is when you realize those were the happy times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:21.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A life ends when you hear the echos of a gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:23.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:25.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,a spirit appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:28.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,without knowledge of what transpired.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.84,0:24:31.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,